Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,growing, developing field, and we learn as we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.94,0:02:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So the initial naivete, and then therefore people who were not able to do it tried to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,do it and said it didn't work, and I couldn't understand why it didn't work because it worked
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:03:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,all the time, and in the video we did called Power Versus Force I think, you know, we used
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,naive children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people say it's suggestion, you know, but in that videotape we used naive children.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't know who Hippocrates was or anybody was, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So a naive child, it worked very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must admit that was an ignorance on my part that I presumed everybody could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's one of the errors of perception is you presume everybody's like yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody is, you know, eager to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for its own sake, and it was a crushing realization that most people do not
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,want to know truth for its own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They really want a verification of what they already believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so that's enough of that rattling on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:04:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my question is I always wanted to know how deep is hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it below the level of consciousness scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you go below there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's extremely low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore it's not really calibratable on that scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other dimensions other than the ones we are familiar with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There are those astral levels, upper, middle, and lower, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are other dimensions, and I don't wish to do a scale for those dimensions, other
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So if a human chooses or keeps choosing, what does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.34,0:04:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If a human chooses or keeps choosing to deny truth and fall in calibration, is there a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,point where they go to so low that one little spark of light has no chance to return?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they're picked up as an easy pickings from other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They call it demonic possession, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it actual life, part of life, or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Different dimension, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Different dimension, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like paradigms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't want to know about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the crime that was revealed about what this guy was going to do to this little girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a week or two ago, you don't want to know where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take my word for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell that I went into was not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It was not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What people depict as hell was the upper level.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, that's just the jacks for openers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The real hell was far, far more horrible than that, but not in a linear way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nonlinear and timeless, and it was not horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was despair at a level of hopelessness that went on forever, and you experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,forever hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons and eons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eons and eons of timeless hopelessness, and it's beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can tell people is you don't want to go there at all, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do not want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not want to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that the intellect does not correlate with the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that intellectually, but in life, I tend to lose track of that fact, so I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.18,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,to know, to help with discernment, if you could talk a little bit about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to talk a little bit about the origin of the intellect?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The origin of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that of course is evolutionary, with the emergence of the prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the advance of hominids, once the hominids stood up, then it had two limbs that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it didn't need for locomotion, and that gave it a tremendous advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the next genetic improvement was the oppositional thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.20,0:07:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you've got an oppositional thumb, you can do tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the emergence of the prefrontal cortex and the gray matter there,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,standing on one's feet and freeing up the front two limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so they were now available for exploration instead of locomotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You could begin to become acquainted with things, and you could now do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the use of tools was very singular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And so when Lucy came around, that was three million years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the beginning of what we call the modern hominid, you know, called man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So would the intellect carry over from one lifetime to the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, dear, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean if you learn algebra in one lifetime, you won't have to learn it next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.71,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take algebra one lifetime, solid geometry the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, I've been working on surrendering the juice of the experiencer as things arise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.72,0:08:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and finding it's a continuous process with seemingly no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a way, I guess I don't understand truly deep surrender to the point where it doesn't come up anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, no, it takes years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget my own evolution of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Persistence is what pays off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.47,0:09:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually it runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you see the peculiar thing about the whole thought of I,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see that the experiencer is trying to constantly fortress the reality of something separate called I.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you say I, in a way you're talking about greediness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Greediness for claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.38,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a whole subject in itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I could write a book, well I started to write a book about it, I did one time, called I, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the I is, I can't write on that, it's some kind of a disc thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.10,0:10:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The I intrinsically is craving, and it claims authorship and ownership.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's constantly looking to reinforce, reforce itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.60,0:10:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason it has to constantly reinforce itself is because it's based on an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was based on a reality, it wouldn't have any interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's always claiming that I did this, I thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The, if you meditate on the concept I, period, just do nothing but hold I, and be with I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-ness, and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, there's nothingness, then, or allness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are concepts, I told you to just stay with I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.24,0:11:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay with I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're elaborating already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay with I-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of it, the feelingness, the location, stay with I-ness, and see what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't call it anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's clustering it all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay with I-ness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.56,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not your thoughts about I, but the essence of I.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will see, it will dissolve, and you'll be left with that out of which I-ness arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll call you Swami, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami-I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that there's a fine line between surrendering everything to God and apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm struggling a bit with, you know, why should I do things, when should I do things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, even when I try to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's futility.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're labeling it as futile, or useless, or not worth anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it means control, surrendering control of it, surrendering control of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,surrendering trying to juice it, allowing everything to just be as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I would just continue to do what I think is right to do, and surrender the outcome?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a neat phrase for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're responsible for the effort, but not the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So result means trying to control, you know, trying to control, say, because you dedicate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your efforts to God, and then whatever is, is whatever is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's karma yoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Karma yoga means selfless service.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not looking at God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not looking for any payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not looking for any gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it for the sake of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.94,0:13:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you do it because you're the steward of certain talents, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a great pianist, you do it because that's your talent, and you're the steward
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of that talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So you give your musicality to the world as a result of your stewardship of that gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, does feeling the sensations of the body play a role in kind of, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,a role in contemplation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something you have to, like, learn how to handle and transcend, just like you do
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.47,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, then you discover the spontaneous, that the body and its functions are spontaneous
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and autonomous, as you let go, trying to control them or resist them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just accept that that's the way that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, a horse is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't try and change the horse, but you accept the nature of the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.42,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you accept the nature of this protoplasmic embodiment, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have to make concessions to the limitations of protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Protoplasm can only stand so much, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So you learn to live within the limitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of the reasons I say it's difficult to be a human, because you have the spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,aspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.57,0:15:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the intellectual concepts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got the emotionality to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got all the yeses and the noes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got all the training, the brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of all that, you've got this pile of protoplasm to look after.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It keeps you busy, you know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're scratching your toe, you're trying to remember your mother-in-law's birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can't remember it, and you feel guilty about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to process that, and just then, you start to sneeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way here this morning, there was something that went right out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was, you know, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably a kitty hair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried pulling it this way, had to go get an eye cup and wash it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what I need as I'm leaving the driveway, you know, is to have to wash your
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,eye out, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, you know, it is difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lordy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever get where we're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we've earned it, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great accomplishment, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to complete a human lifetime,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and it really is demanding on so many levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, you had said before
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,that sometimes God uses our minds to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.91,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we tell the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,between when it is God who is using our mind to think
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and when we are doing our own chatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's sort of a languaging problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say realizations
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that are benevolent and holistic
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and tend to heal, etc.,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.80,0:17:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,one could ascribe them as coming from a higher source.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be God personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But the radiance of that energy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,favor thoughts of a certain direction
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and not favor thoughts in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I never see it as causation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it as likelihood, potentiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the intention of becoming spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,increases the potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that certain thoughts are going to be more common
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,than they would be in a person who lacks that intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But they're not caused by the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.41,0:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality rather than likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really, in a way, physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Advanced theoretical physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The question that I had was in reference
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to something that I read in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Transcending the Levels of Consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about surrender and devotion and faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.58,0:18:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would just like for you to,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if you would, expand a little bit on the faith
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and its faith in what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith is an aspect of personality
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,without which we can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.16,0:18:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,without which you couldn't live, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have faith in all kinds of things all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you put your foot down,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you have faith that your ankle's gonna hold you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So faith is really operative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with expectation and expected reliability.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything except write my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, spiritual faith is something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing your faith and hope in things unseen is trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's really trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Placing your faith in things unseen, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,comes as an inspiration to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, to do that already increases the likelihood
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.16,0:19:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,of the fulfillment of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Not from a causal viewpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you have the likelihood of it is increased
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,by your commitment and your intention
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that the response is going to be
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,more positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,More probable in a certain direction than another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're affecting probability by intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:20:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, trusting that the paths in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teachers that were the way-showers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That that's a safe path to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the faith that you're talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we go even farther than faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we look at the modern mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The modern mind would like some kind of mathematical
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,or logical or intellectual proof as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They would like to have it backed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.44,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith, without good works, you know, is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, faith for its own sake, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is already a certain kind of sacredness, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.78,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're not looking for payoffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's sort of like karma yoga
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.72,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,in that you do it for its own sake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and not for some gain, to be gained by thereby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But thereby you fulfill your own potential to evolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:21:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The skeptic has no belief in faith at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.96,0:21:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He ridicules faith, except in his own skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has great faith in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I get a kick out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.25,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know there's that saying that God has a,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it, tell God you have a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and what is the sense of humor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell God you have a plan and then everything just gets messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And today I plan to go into the, on top of that, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.96,0:21:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on Shelby Road the other way
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and just sit up there and contemplate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then for some reason Tim picked up a book
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I thought this was a humorous book
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this Scorpion book
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,well it changed my experience sitting up in the Red Rocks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.42,0:21:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,that was quite overwhelming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I wanted to share with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that somehow the self gets me here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure how that happens
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because I get in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.21,0:22:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and I really have a hard time functioning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a hard time what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.55,0:22:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,who asked you to function?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.76,0:22:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,she just asks questions
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but yet I crave this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hike in the mornings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I get out there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,or how I get back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm always by myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.80,0:22:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there's not an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and my spiritual stuff is kind of private
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but then I get in your presence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I come here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.72,0:22:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just crave coming into this energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.58,0:22:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I just want to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.53,0:22:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all I know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.15,0:22:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't really have a question or a story or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.79,0:22:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,that's very common
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.85,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,because you come with a question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.85,0:22:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a certain energy field
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the question dissolves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.05,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not a question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know I don't even have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.99,0:23:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where I have
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,where it's familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and people understand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your own intention
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you reflect that fact like a pool
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.69,0:23:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that ripples in a pool to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that's your own self
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.41,0:23:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,bouncing off of myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.54,0:23:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,so now you're only experiencing your own self
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,well
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.62,0:23:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,this happens when I get around you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.98,0:23:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a seminar with you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.98,0:23:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,it was in Palm Springs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're usually wired up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and you didn't ever leave the stage before
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was sitting on a row seat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had my eyes closed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.90,0:23:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just sort of taking your energy in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,with my eyes closed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had goosebumps on my arms
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the hair on my neck went up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.90,0:23:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I started having problems breathing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I was getting teary
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.90,0:23:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I finally opened my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,like what is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.90,0:23:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and you were standing next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and every time I get in this presence
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,this happens
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.80,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is a phenomena
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.80,0:24:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.80,0:24:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.80,0:24:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what I would do without you
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.80,0:24:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's autonomous
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.80,0:24:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it occurs in the spiritual world
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.80,0:24:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's autonomous
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it happens of its own
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I would do without your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.80,0:24:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,because I would be
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.21,0:24:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they're wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.21,0:24:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,they just help me know
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going on in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and I go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.21,0:24:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,oh that's what's important
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that's because of who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.21,0:24:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.21,0:24:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were somebody else
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.21,0:24:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd think I'm a nuisance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.85,0:24:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am like
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.93,0:24:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.93,0:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I put your video going
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.93,0:24:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and I go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.93,0:24:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you God
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.93,0:24:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you for this man
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.93,0:24:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,God thank you for this man
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.93,0:24:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,everything makes sense
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.93,0:24:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,when I listen to your words
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.93,0:24:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so thank you God
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.93,0:24:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're aligned with divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.93,0:24:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,in this way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.93,0:24:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.93,0:24:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if you were not with baseball
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.93,0:24:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't feel that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.93,0:24:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not much on the ball field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.37,0:24:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see the ball coming at me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.68,0:24:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's why they
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.68,0:24:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't let me on the field
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.68,0:24:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.68,0:24:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much for your books
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.68,0:25:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I live to read them every day
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.68,0:25:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and they've certainly transformed my life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.68,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,right now I'm dealing with something
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.68,0:25:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have dealt with
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and perhaps I can gain some insight
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.68,0:25:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,from you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.68,0:25:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how to go about
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.68,0:25:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,dealing with this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,with chronic pain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.68,0:25:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and potential
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.68,0:25:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a great potential
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.68,0:25:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for physical disability
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.68,0:25:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems inevitable
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.68,0:25:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've tried a lot of things
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.68,0:25:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,allopathic
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.68,0:25:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and alternative medicine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.68,0:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and it seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.68,0:25:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,a degenerative process
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.68,0:25:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,so you know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.68,0:25:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,being very galvanized
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.68,0:25:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're mentally degenerating
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.68,0:25:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,mentally degenerating
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.68,0:25:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,on top of it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.68,0:25:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,good luck to you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.68,0:25:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,right
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.68,0:25:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happy imbecile
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.68,0:25:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.68,0:25:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.68,0:25:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I'd like to be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.68,0:25:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is happily
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.68,0:25:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.68,0:25:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.68,0:25:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.71,0:25:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.71,0:25:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.71,0:25:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.71,0:25:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.71,0:25:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.71,0:25:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is happily in pain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.71,0:25:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is it possible
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,how does
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.71,0:25:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what I'm asking
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.71,0:25:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.71,0:25:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,transcended
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.71,0:25:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,pain
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.71,0:25:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.71,0:25:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I would not put myself
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.83,0:25:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at the same level
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.71,0:25:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.71,0:25:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that I could
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.71,0:25:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but are there any directions
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.71,0:25:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for dealing with it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.71,0:25:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,so that you can actually
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.71,0:25:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,function in life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.71,0:25:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and do things
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.71,0:26:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,other than
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.71,0:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't label it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.71,0:26:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,pain anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.71,0:26:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not experiencing pain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.81,0:26:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,pain is a concept
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.81,0:26:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,a thought
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.81,0:26:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.81,0:26:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,there are certain sensations
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.87,0:26:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,coming up
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.87,0:26:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,what you do is you completely surrender and let go any resistance you become one
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.75,0:26:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with the sensation and you thereby disappear them because you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.50,0:26:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,experience that which is not resisted so I've tried that I didn't say this is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.52,0:26:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,taking me years but just that's the idea is to constantly surrender also clear
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.52,0:26:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,anything in yourself that you think suspect karmically might be an
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.02,0:26:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,underpinning of it you understand what I'm saying when you say surrender do you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:27:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,mean somehow forgive it within yourself admit it thank you I think that answers
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.48,0:27:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it I will proceed and hope it all just dissolves away
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.38,0:27:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,next time I see you sometimes the serious thing to do is to ask for
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.53,0:27:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness for that within within yourself of which you no longer recall
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.31,0:27:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,which brought such things to others well Lord forgive me for having brought
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.81,0:27:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,suffering pain into the life of others sometimes I think out of guilt out of
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.40,0:27:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the pain you've brought into the life of others which you've forgotten you bring
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.30,0:27:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it upon yourself and once you forgive yourself for that tends to receive
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.66,0:27:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,forgiveness and a POWERFULness all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.22,0:27:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's kind of the fire I'm looking at you different and I thought well you know
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.36,0:28:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,he's you're big in real life you're like this
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.01,0:28:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I am a baby compared to midgets yes that's why I like going to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.21,0:28:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Korea everybody was my height
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.07,0:28:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, I felt like a big man. I looked down and everybody was about the same level I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.07,0:28:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.07,0:28:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is neat. This is like a six-footer must feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.07,0:28:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.07,0:28:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, my sister wanted to say she loves you a lot, and thank you very much because you changed her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.07,0:28:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And all she's read is Power vs. Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.07,0:28:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And also friends from Maui, Hawaii send their love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.07,0:28:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.20,0:29:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, you often talk about having stewardship of one's gifts and one's assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.87,0:29:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What if all you have is debt and you don't know what your gifts are?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.87,0:29:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.87,0:29:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't know what your gifts are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.87,0:29:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to begin with, debts, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.30,0:29:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because debts become a motivator, do they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.35,0:29:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't want to have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.48,0:29:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do debts mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.48,0:29:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do debts lead you to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.70,0:29:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.54,0:29:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.54,0:29:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.21,0:29:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Broccoli say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.21,0:29:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.21,0:29:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.98,0:29:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sitting in my study and all of a sudden Broccoli would go, go to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.30,0:29:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.30,0:29:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Brings me up every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.36,0:29:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.36,0:29:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's actually, it's not the debts that are the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.36,0:29:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.36,0:29:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The debts themselves are just the debts.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.36,0:29:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They come, they go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:29:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.36,0:29:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more not really having an idea of what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,An idea of what the gifts are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.36,0:30:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, stewardship of one's gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.36,0:30:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would love to be a steward of my gifts, but I don't know what they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.36,0:30:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.36,0:30:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure I do somewhere, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.36,0:30:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a gift therapist, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.36,0:30:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my gift therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.36,0:30:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You got nice teeth?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.36,0:30:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You still got your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.36,0:30:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't had plastic surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.36,0:30:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.36,0:30:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a new nose made out of cartilage from your knee?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.36,0:30:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.36,0:30:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all, it's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.36,0:30:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you don't wear glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.36,0:30:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had surgery there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.36,0:30:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.36,0:30:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.36,0:30:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.36,0:30:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.36,0:30:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.36,0:30:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.36,0:30:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.36,0:30:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.36,0:30:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the LASIK surgery there.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.26,0:30:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you see all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.26,0:30:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I see pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.26,0:30:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.26,0:30:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you got a full head of hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.26,0:30:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.26,0:30:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have carcinoma anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.26,0:30:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't even know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.26,0:30:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have health, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.26,0:30:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.26,0:30:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.26,0:30:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.26,0:30:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.26,0:30:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.26,0:30:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have pain, but yeah, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.26,0:30:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You have...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.26,0:30:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have physical aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.52,0:30:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.52,0:30:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Forty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.52,0:30:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.52,0:30:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you still have youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.52,0:30:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.68,0:30:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, but as far as I'm concerned, I don't have any physical aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.68,0:31:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.68,0:31:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have aliveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.68,0:31:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have health.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.68,0:31:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.68,0:31:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.68,0:31:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.68,0:31:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.68,0:31:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.68,0:31:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good golly, what more do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.68,0:31:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't want gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.68,0:31:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You got friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.68,0:31:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, wonderful, beautiful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.68,0:31:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, is there something more beyond the lens?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.68,0:31:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess what I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.68,0:31:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to understand is it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.68,0:31:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably thinking of a special person.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.68,0:31:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.68,0:31:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.68,0:31:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.90,0:31:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.90,0:31:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.90,0:31:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.90,0:31:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.90,0:31:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.90,0:31:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.90,0:31:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.90,0:31:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.90,0:31:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.03,0:31:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.03,0:31:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.03,0:31:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.03,0:31:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.03,0:31:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.03,0:31:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.03,0:31:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.03,0:31:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.41,0:31:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.48,0:31:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.48,0:31:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.48,0:31:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.76,0:31:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.76,0:31:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.76,0:31:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.76,0:31:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.76,0:31:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.76,0:31:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.76,0:31:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.76,0:31:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,More of like, a way of being of service in the world as...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.76,0:31:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like, is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.76,0:31:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to do, is just do what I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.76,0:31:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like there's so much more...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.76,0:31:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.76,0:31:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're friendly and kind and benign to the world, think how exceptional you are already.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.76,0:31:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember from that chart in the pyramid?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.86,0:31:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.86,0:32:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,of the people in the world just to be benign and kind and friendly and open and helpful helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.27,0:32:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,little ladies crossing the street you know what i'm saying yeah i do always take a little while
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.26,0:32:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,begin to label these so you think it gives us something exceptional maybe that's the thing
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.54,0:32:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah it's all dark and handsome and rich you see a famous movie star i guess i just feel like like
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,i like um you have good health you walk around you've got a pacemaker i mean you're way ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,of the game i guess it's in striving to do in striving to do more that's all it's just wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.98,0:32:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a better person well the intention is sufficient and then you ask god to reveal to you
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.40,0:33:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,more okay you're trying to use your thinker to get it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.40,0:33:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,forget it
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thinker. That which you are is your gift to the world. You understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.71,0:33:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.71,0:33:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you safe to be in a boat with?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.74,0:33:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.74,0:33:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't stand up in a canoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.74,0:33:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.74,0:33:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way ahead of the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.79,0:33:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have a charming smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.79,0:33:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to say that I've been reading your books a lot. I'm up to the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.74,0:33:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The growth between ten years ago and now is phenomenal because I was reading people like Thomas Troward and Ralph Waldo Emerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.74,0:34:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a religious scientist and practitioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.74,0:34:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I'm teaching that class and now I actually understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.74,0:34:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.96,0:34:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it was like I did it because I had to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.96,0:34:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's just,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.96,0:34:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You get meaning behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.96,0:34:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.96,0:34:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.96,0:34:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,These teachings have made very clear things that were so confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.96,0:34:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm able to actually hold a line of thought until the end of the sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.96,0:34:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That may sound like amazing, but because of your type of writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.96,0:34:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now transcendentalism means more to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.60,0:34:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, this is, I don't know if it's a question or it's just a confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.86,0:34:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.86,0:34:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been involved in NLP and timeline therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.86,0:34:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if you know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.86,0:34:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a teaching derived from Huna.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.86,0:34:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been doing a workshop,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.86,0:34:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,which I vowed back 13 years ago to do at least one a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.86,0:34:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's about emotional freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.05,0:34:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And the name of my workshop is Emotional Freedom by Giving Yourself a Second Opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.05,0:35:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So I do this and I do this with my church group.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.05,0:35:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just wondering,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.05,0:35:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.05,0:35:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm just going to ask you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's karmic consequences
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.40,0:35:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,for everything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.40,0:35:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.40,0:35:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And, but then again, there was,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.40,0:35:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you say today that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.40,0:35:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not exactly tit for tat or life for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.40,0:35:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not cause and effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.40,0:35:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.40,0:35:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likelihood and potentialities.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.40,0:35:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Okay, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.40,0:35:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I'm thinking if you work with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.40,0:35:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and they release a lot of karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.40,0:35:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and they don't have to go the whole tit for tat route,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.40,0:35:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.63,0:35:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.63,0:35:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.17,0:35:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.17,0:35:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we only have it to be done with their willingness and their assent.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.17,0:35:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not doing it against their will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.17,0:35:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.17,0:35:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's absolutely the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.17,0:35:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.17,0:35:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.59,0:35:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.59,0:35:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doing another two workshops this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.59,0:35:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.59,0:35:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.59,0:35:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.91,0:35:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.91,0:36:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,God in his ultimate mercy gives us a chance to undo our errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.91,0:36:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.91,0:36:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.91,0:36:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.94,0:36:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.94,0:36:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move faster then.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.04,0:36:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.84,0:36:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.19,0:36:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.19,0:36:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.19,0:36:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So in all of your books you have them calibrated by chapter,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.19,0:36:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,except for transcending.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.60,0:36:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because each chapter is already about a calibrated level.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.60,0:36:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.60,0:36:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So then even though the lower calibrated chapters would still calibrate low?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.37,0:36:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.37,0:36:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a separate number.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.37,0:36:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I mean the description, the analysis of it would be of a different calibration.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.56,0:36:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.56,0:36:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.56,0:36:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.56,0:36:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just thought that was really curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.56,0:37:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I like the fact that each, like in the first one, power versus force, you talked
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.36,0:37:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,about how you went through each paragraph and sentence and discovered like the one with
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.36,0:37:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the John Lennon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.36,0:37:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Line and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.36,0:37:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.36,0:37:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really interesting because I have, kinesiology is very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.36,0:37:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.36,0:37:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.36,0:37:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've enjoyed your books very much and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.36,0:37:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.36,0:37:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.36,0:37:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.36,0:37:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,From the Chicago area.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.36,0:37:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I'm part of a group that promotes, you know, it's a spiritual, a new spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.36,0:37:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,group that talks about your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.40,0:37:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I brought you a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.40,0:37:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a book I wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.40,0:37:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.40,0:37:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicated to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.62,0:37:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.62,0:37:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.62,0:37:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.62,0:37:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.62,0:37:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.62,0:37:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.62,0:37:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.62,0:37:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.62,0:38:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.62,0:38:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.62,0:38:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And a question I had for you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.00,0:38:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.00,0:38:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.29,0:38:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.17,0:38:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a hug?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.49,0:38:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hug my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.49,0:38:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.49,0:38:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.49,0:38:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.49,0:38:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all my bones have turned to Styrofoam.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.49,0:38:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.00,0:38:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.45,0:38:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.19,0:38:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I'm doing everything to recalcify the skillet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.14,0:38:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I never paid much attention to the body, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.87,0:38:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've done a lot more work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.15,0:38:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and now I'm learning you've got to pay attention to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.90,0:38:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise it's going to be a drag.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.35,0:38:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand all the bad things I put in this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.15,0:38:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.29,0:38:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get a picture with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.69,0:38:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.47,0:38:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.48,0:39:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.94,0:39:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond words.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.29,0:39:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is about devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.06,0:39:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.80,0:39:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And for me, how to live on the razor's edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.56,0:39:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From your teachings, the opening, letting go into the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.04,0:39:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the spontaneity emerging, all the beauty, desire for enlightenment, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.87,0:39:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The city, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.51,0:39:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.05,0:39:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And recently, as I've been dealing,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.56,0:39:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been deeply quiet, spontaneously, I reach a place inside
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.56,0:40:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,where I think I've met the essence of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.44,0:40:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the density that doesn't surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.37,0:40:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.00,0:40:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.22,0:40:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.14,0:40:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the razor's edge?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.28,0:40:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You follow the razor's edge, and it'll take it to the core of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.76,0:40:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the ego's belief that it is your creator,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and your source of life, and you surrender that to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.04,0:40:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you go through a period that you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.43,0:40:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm anywhere close to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, honey, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.87,0:40:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a whole evolutionary phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.11,0:40:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not linear, so you can't say,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.41,0:40:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,well, if you're here, now this is coming next.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.95,0:41:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like fields interacting with fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.49,0:41:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So this field here potentiates all the fields within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.15,0:41:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this field is this way, and this field is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.27,0:41:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the field is empowering every one of these fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So if this is empowered this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.69,0:41:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's even more this way than it would have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.77,0:41:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's overlapping coexistence fields of influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.91,0:41:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more like a complicated interaction of fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.35,0:41:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you did that, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.69,0:41:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.39,0:41:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.27,0:41:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihoods, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.67,0:41:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So each field is a potentializing,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.23,0:41:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are multiple interacting fields co-influencing phenomena,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.40,0:41:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from not only the past, but the present,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.82,0:41:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from fields beyond fields beyond fields,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.20,0:42:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,beyond which is divinity itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.48,0:42:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite omnipresent field,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.49,0:42:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which empowers all the lesser fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.17,0:42:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.78,0:42:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.94,0:42:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.20,0:42:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.90,0:42:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep doing what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.36,0:42:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.32,0:42:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.58,0:42:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Fields within fields within fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.69,0:42:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you close the doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.09,0:42:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're losing our air conditioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.74,0:42:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.37,0:42:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've enjoyed your work for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.45,0:42:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time for me to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.77,0:42:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very pleased and excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.16,0:42:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank both of you and your team.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.52,0:42:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is quite a bit of experience in living in a communal setting,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.36,0:42:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.15,0:42:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exquisite for all that you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.87,0:42:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and the details I have great appreciation for.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.97,0:43:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my whole life been highly interested in spiritual evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.79,0:43:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And one of the things that has caught my passion for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.88,0:43:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the major religions, there is reference to the Golden Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.16,0:43:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden Age?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.34,0:43:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Golden Age, which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.12,0:43:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Historical age, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.68,0:43:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It means going back before the fall of man,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.14,0:43:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,where...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.50,0:43:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.98,0:43:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.10,0:43:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.14,0:43:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where humanity functioned in full consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.14,0:43:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,full divine function.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.63,0:43:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder, especially with what you bring,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.68,0:43:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,if this awakening that I am going through and we're going through
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.82,0:43:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is a gateway of some sort to bring back this Golden Age,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.37,0:43:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,not like it used to be, but in a new way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.46,0:44:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to presume that.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.38,0:44:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The previous age was...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.80,0:44:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was vulnerable, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.42,0:44:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to recreate that which failed the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.62,0:44:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.62,0:44:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like a future where the fall of man is not a potentiality or even a likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.99,0:44:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.99,0:44:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.59,0:44:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.49,0:44:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Past is all illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.69,0:44:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego was the cause of the fall, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.86,0:44:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.86,0:44:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to create which was, which failed miserably?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.68,0:44:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.68,0:44:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.68,0:44:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to create that which is immune to.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.68,0:44:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.68,0:45:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.97,0:45:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,negativity and temptation and ignorance.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.97,0:45:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the naivete of Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.97,0:45:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,number of years now and I wondered if you're planning to have a lecture series
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.40,0:45:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,next year. We're in the planning stage of next year. This year we're trying as
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.09,0:45:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,every other month. We'll probably still do every other month and then the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.67,0:45:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,workshop in the month in between. That was that everybody liked that a great
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.38,0:45:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,deal. Real old-fashioned sad saying you know question answer discourse. I like
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.88,0:46:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,walking through the crowd and having a spontaneous conversation with everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.42,0:46:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I like the best. How about books? How about books? Books I'm planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.86,0:46:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Yes I told you we're doing an atlas of a hundred charts. We have lectures on
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.88,0:46:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,healing and recovery which is gonna be out probably after the devotional nonduality.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.20,0:46:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's spirituality and modern land.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.93,0:46:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.12,0:46:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the old-fashioned religion doesn't appeal to modern man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.48,0:46:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither does skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.74,0:46:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Skepticism does not fulfill him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.74,0:46:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.54,0:46:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,These men are feeling unsatisfied and unfulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.11,0:46:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So what would be a spiritual pathway for a modern man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.17,0:46:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who isn't a peasant tending sheep on the desert 3,000 or 4,000 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.84,0:47:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What appealed to him is idiotic to the modern man.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.12,0:47:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bush lit up and started talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.86,0:47:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.48,0:47:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Swallowed by a whale in, say, three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.68,0:47:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, come on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.34,0:47:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So this forthcoming book is going to be a takeoff from the Scopes trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.60,0:47:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scopes trial was never resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.56,0:47:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They never resolved the argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.22,0:47:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They simply avoided addressing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.96,0:47:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He attacked his character.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.76,0:47:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The question was never answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.86,0:47:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What can modern man hold on to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.48,0:47:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and not look like an idiot through old-fashioned religion?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be intelligent, scientific,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.28,0:47:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and also spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.30,0:47:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and religious?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.98,0:47:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's modern man's dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.98,0:47:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the problem I tend to address.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.82,0:47:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to pick it up from the Scopes trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.20,0:47:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which is in the 20s,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.86,0:47:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody has answered it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.70,0:47:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.02,0:47:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to pick one way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.72,0:47:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.26,0:48:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do a picture with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.68,0:48:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.89,0:48:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.81,0:48:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Old-fashioned religion,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.37,0:48:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,which appeals to the scientific mind
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.93,0:48:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is to the ignorant dummies out in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.99,0:48:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,rustic folks,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.02,0:48:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,or else scientific skepticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.92,0:48:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, where is the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.16,0:48:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that embraces modern man?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.72,0:48:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.58,0:48:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.12,0:48:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.83,0:48:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm eager to write right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.35,0:48:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything else that gets in the way of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.35,0:48:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impatient to get through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.19,0:48:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.76,0:48:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you would be willing
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.30,0:48:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.64,0:48:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.02,0:48:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.64,0:48:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Generally, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.96,0:48:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.56,0:48:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I do have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.12,0:48:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When you talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.25,0:49:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember which book it's in now,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.25,0:49:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but no need to do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.18,0:49:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the causality that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.92,0:49:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to meditate,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.50,0:49:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,no need to be an activist
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.85,0:49:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,for change in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.47,0:49:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What motivates us?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.99,0:49:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How do we maintain motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.35,0:49:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're quoting.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.44,0:49:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You say no need for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.98,0:49:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.98,0:49:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.40,0:49:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was one of your...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.32,0:49:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're describing passivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.04,0:49:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my perception of what I read,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.00,0:49:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,so it very likely was misperceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.68,0:49:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering a thing to God
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.98,0:49:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same thing as apathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.06,0:49:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're accountable for is the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.28,0:49:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.58,0:49:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The result is up to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.86,0:49:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do what you can to help people help themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.14,0:49:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and now it's up to them
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.38,0:49:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,because you don't want the karmic responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.82,0:50:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,or controlling other people as far as outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.56,0:50:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can lead them to water,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.48,0:50:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you can't make them drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.82,0:50:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a horse's karma whether he drinks or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.88,0:50:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your karma is really to provide the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.56,0:50:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's defining what is your responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.40,0:50:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,towards yourself and others.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.08,0:50:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.90,0:50:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To give yourself and others the best opportunity you can
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.92,0:50:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,for the highest level of love that you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.16,0:50:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the most loving thing is to let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.25,0:50:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.07,0:50:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.17,0:50:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.93,0:50:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.65,0:50:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let them be.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.41,0:50:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about surfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.25,0:50:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's sort of like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.05,0:50:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Living in causality is like surfing life.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.23,0:50:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.59,0:50:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Surfing is very much like surfing.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.31,0:50:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.89,0:50:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.25,0:50:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to move you because you're right in that light.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.89,0:50:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What light?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.05,0:50:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.17,0:50:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to move this light just slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.17,0:50:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.76,0:50:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a filming thing, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.28,0:50:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.98,0:51:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop, hop, hop, hop.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.17,0:51:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.00,0:51:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,When I first found your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.18,0:51:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it started to smooth out my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.28,0:51:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And fill in a lot of the gaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.60,0:51:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I went along a little further.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.55,0:51:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, just about every aspect is in complete and total upheaval.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.81,0:51:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, being here, I think I've heard this story now from some other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.71,0:51:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.88,0:51:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly sure how to go forward every day, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.42,0:51:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You just follow basic spiritual principles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.46,0:51:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.22,0:51:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My hardest role, or what I perceive to be my hardest role right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.15,0:51:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is the mother of a 16-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.66,0:51:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.58,0:51:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is my third child.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.96,0:52:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew what I was doing until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.69,0:52:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that I'm in such upheaval and everything changing in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.52,0:52:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and in these roles,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.08,0:52:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking to see if anybody has any questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.76,0:52:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.86,0:52:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.96,0:52:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.02,0:52:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.12,0:52:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.16,0:52:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has any wisdom, because I'm having difficulty understanding and parenting, where you stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.58,0:52:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where you kind of stop, you know, where you start turning it over to them, and let them
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.51,0:52:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,live their life, and not, because I don't have the answers anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.62,0:52:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.67,0:52:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very mysterious about all this, I mean, what are you talking about, big turns, your
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.07,0:52:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,life is all topsy-turvy about life?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.43,0:52:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, you know, everything has changed my...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.93,0:52:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.45,0:52:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Religious affiliation, where I live, my relationship with my husband, every person in my family,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.94,0:53:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,all the people that I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.18,0:53:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it's like getting a divorce, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.46,0:53:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally changes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.46,0:53:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the whole, everything, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.42,0:53:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quitting a job, moving to a different country.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.34,0:53:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, it feels like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.76,0:53:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so what's your question, is what is the role of a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.26,0:53:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, a parent who's going through all this, who's now having trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.91,0:53:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where the answers were simple before, they've gotten so much more complex, and I just wondered
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.51,0:53:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.51,0:53:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a therapist?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.51,0:53:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.51,0:53:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.47,0:53:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.47,0:53:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.47,0:53:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Practically.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.47,0:53:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're honest with a 16-year-old, you just tell him, I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.47,0:53:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The practicality is that I only have a therapist, I mean, the complexity you're describing,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.56,0:53:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what's the role of a parent?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.16,0:53:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.16,0:53:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to try and influence a kid in a certain direction without controlling them, but I
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.75,0:53:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,really think a therapist would be helpful to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.87,0:53:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.35,0:54:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very true.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.35,0:54:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.35,0:54:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I needed to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.35,0:54:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really psychological, emotional, not spiritual, really, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.46,0:54:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Adjustment problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.46,0:54:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.78,0:54:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.78,0:54:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual seems to have stirred it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.78,0:54:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.49,0:54:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.49,0:54:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.49,0:54:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you're going through...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.78,0:54:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that going through it isn't easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.57,0:54:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.57,0:54:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.57,0:54:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.57,0:54:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention is to do the best you can in all these various roles.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.76,0:54:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.76,0:54:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But you need somebody that you can give feedback about the details, and not generalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.76,0:54:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, with me here, you're going to have to do a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.76,0:54:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.76,0:54:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.76,0:54:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.76,0:54:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.76,0:54:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.76,0:54:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.76,0:54:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.76,0:54:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.76,0:54:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.76,0:54:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.76,0:54:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.76,0:54:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.76,0:54:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.08,0:54:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.08,0:54:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.08,0:54:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.59,0:54:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.59,0:54:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.59,0:54:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.59,0:54:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it piecemeal, piece by piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.59,0:54:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.59,0:54:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.59,0:54:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.59,0:54:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.59,0:54:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.59,0:54:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.17,0:54:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.90,0:54:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.90,0:54:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.90,0:54:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.90,0:54:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There are certain times in your life when having a therapist is like having a best
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.90,0:55:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,friend, and it's somebody you can trust and discuss things with, and discuss it at a
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.90,0:55:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,different level than personal relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.90,0:55:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.90,0:55:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi. My question was about what exactly is your level of consciousness? Is it like an average of all your attributes or is it one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.39,0:55:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Overall field, yeah. That's what I thought. It was just at a study group we were having a conversation and there were some disagreements so I thought I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.39,0:55:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, different archetypal roles within yourself may have evolved to different levels. The student in you might be quite involved. The devotee might be quite involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.39,0:55:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So the various roles that you have within yourself, some will be more advanced than others, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.55,0:55:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you calibrated them differently, you know, my social person, what does it calibrate at? What does my student calibrate at?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.74,0:56:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You might find yourself more advanced.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.74,0:56:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your student is quite far advanced. Your social person is retarded. It might be the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.74,0:56:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a cool extrovert, but when it comes to studentship, you know, you're not well-motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.74,0:56:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could examine different aspects of your personality and calibrate them independently.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.90,0:56:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it'd be fun to get to know, you know, where are your high points and where are your low points. Are you familiar with Carl Jung and the, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.00,0:56:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.00,0:56:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.00,0:56:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.00,0:56:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You could look at the different aspects of your personality. What's the calibrated level of your friend, you know, being the friend to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.00,0:56:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The student, the son, the lover, the various roles that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.38,0:56:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How good a neighbor are you? You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.38,0:56:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.38,0:56:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, there are people, there are neighbors so bad that people shoot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.38,0:57:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure hope I'm not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.42,0:57:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a guy, an old man who lived in an apartment, he was 90, in New York City, and the SOB next door would not stop playing his radio loud at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.42,0:57:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So he took a shotgun and killed him dead in a mackerel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.06,0:57:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So the guy who played the radio loud was not being a good neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.06,0:57:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he is. He's a very quiet neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.02,0:57:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I sympathize with the old guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.37,0:57:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.37,0:57:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably deserved it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.42,0:57:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You often talk about when a person reaches a level of 600 and half of them decide not to stay and half of them stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.42,0:57:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.42,0:58:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if this S and so forth is 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.45,0:58:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is 600 and it dies and goes to the other side, the body dies, then does the body have to come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.45,0:58:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.45,0:58:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.45,0:58:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the body shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.45,0:58:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's a free elective. It's a free elective.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.45,0:58:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a free elective.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.45,0:58:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very clear that there's no obligation in any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.74,0:58:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.74,0:58:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no gain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.74,0:58:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gained and nothing lost in either direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.95,0:58:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.95,0:58:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.07,0:58:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.64,0:58:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.09,0:58:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's an open door.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.59,0:58:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to walk through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.59,0:58:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That is very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.59,0:58:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.46,0:58:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.46,0:59:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you about deja vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.18,0:59:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an explanation for it because I haven't looked at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.49,0:59:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether it's a neurological doubling back and it's an illusion that you've experienced it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.24,0:59:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it a couple of times.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.24,0:59:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it a couple of times in my life and it was quite real.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.36,0:59:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The certainty that you've experienced this before, whereas in fact I know it was not
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.46,0:59:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,possible, but the experiential was that you've experienced this exactly before.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.65,0:59:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the clock being at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.65,0:59:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an explanation because I haven't really researched it.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.11,0:59:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm suspecting it's some kind of a time doubling illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.46,0:59:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just suspecting that neurologically.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.46,1:00:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So something just don't necessarily pay attention to?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.42,1:00:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.42,1:00:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.42,1:00:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've had it and it's very real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.42,1:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it seems real.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.42,1:00:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I had it in World War II when I was on the troop ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.42,1:00:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The train broke down in Golden, Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.42,1:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It took four hours to fix it, the whole troop train.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.00,1:00:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We all got off.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.10,1:00:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We got to be back four hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.10,1:00:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked to the center of town.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.10,1:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There in the center of town, you look down all four directions in Golden, Colorado.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.10,1:00:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a mountain at the end of each one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.10,1:00:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On this corner, there's a great big clock like you see in front of a jeweler's clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.13,1:00:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced that before, and yet I'd never been west of the Mississippi.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.13,1:00:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was very vivid.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.38,1:00:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So I know what deja vu is like.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.38,1:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.96,1:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.96,1:00:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.40,1:01:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the final doorway that you write about in the book, I.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.40,1:01:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that calibrated?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.40,1:01:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.40,1:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.40,1:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that at level 600 or 850?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.62,1:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Final doorway is at 970.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.62,1:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said final, I mean final.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.68,1:01:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because for a long time, I was under the impression that it calibrated at 600 because you state
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.80,1:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that like Nisargadatta Maharaj went through it, and it seemed unclear that...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.80,1:01:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because his calibrated level of consciousness was like 720.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.18,1:01:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the final doorway.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.82,1:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Final doorway, you give up life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.20,1:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They gave up their perception of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.31,1:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And they surrendered their perception of life to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.40,1:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.40,1:02:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But not life itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.35,1:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Not what the ego believes is life itself, the source of its life.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.80,1:02:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.80,1:02:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.75,1:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.75,1:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a college student right now, and I'm surrounded by a lot of alcohol and kind of like a party
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.75,1:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,environment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.75,1:02:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Party environment.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.75,1:02:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a college student.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.75,1:02:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.75,1:02:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Party environment, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.75,1:02:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.75,1:02:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So my question is, how can you be in that environment and be kind and loving without
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.75,1:02:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,being taken advantage of at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.38,1:02:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind and loving doesn't mean passive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.38,1:02:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean being a patsy.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.47,1:02:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It means camaraderie and then drawing lines when they're going to go too far.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.35,1:02:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If, let's say, someone keeps peer pressuring you, and finally you just tell them, like,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.35,1:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,no, is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.35,1:02:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody keeps pressuring you?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.35,1:03:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, if you're firm, is that...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.35,1:03:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you tell them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.35,1:03:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Still being kind?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.35,1:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go along with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.35,1:03:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go along with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.35,1:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.48,1:03:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand it, but I myself can't go along with it behaviorally, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.48,1:03:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.41,1:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We all have our own...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.41,1:03:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The way we were brought up, you know, we have our own inbuilt conscience.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.41,1:03:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's certain things you just can't do and live with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.41,1:03:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.41,1:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, look, I could do it, but then I'd have difficulty with myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.23,1:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, what I meant more was, like, when you're saying no, it's not the actual alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.23,1:03:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just mean if someone was saying something to you and they're kind of pushing you, kind
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.23,1:03:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of pushing your limit, is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.23,1:03:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how you're kind of firm a lot of times when you say no?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.23,1:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.23,1:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.23,1:03:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.23,1:03:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.23,1:03:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.23,1:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.23,1:03:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.23,1:03:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.23,1:03:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.23,1:03:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to be firm?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.23,1:03:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that still...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.23,1:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.23,1:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You just say, you know, I can't go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.23,1:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.23,1:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.23,1:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Limits.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.23,1:03:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard being...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.23,1:03:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Limits, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.23,1:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Limits.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.23,1:03:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was about surrender, and you've already answered it, so I just wanted to come
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.23,1:03:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,up and say thank you for the changes in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.23,1:03:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.23,1:03:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.23,1:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.36,1:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.22,1:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.22,1:03:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.22,1:03:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.07,1:03:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.07,1:03:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.19,1:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.19,1:04:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.19,1:04:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.19,1:04:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.19,1:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.19,1:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.19,1:04:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.19,1:04:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.19,1:04:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.19,1:04:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,caused by the books and tapes you've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.67,1:04:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.29,1:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.62,1:04:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the most yellow yellow I've seen all day.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.84,1:04:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that yellow or is that yellow?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.80,1:04:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She's like a walking dandelion.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.54,1:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Electric yellow.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.22,1:04:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I had figured out how to ask this a minute ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.65,1:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't quite now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.09,1:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm the guy that doesn't step on the bugs
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.60,1:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and picks the dead animals off the road
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.08,1:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because I don't like seeing them squished.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.74,1:04:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So then I get this opportunity for a job
Dialogue: 0,1:04:53.77,1:04:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that entails protecting the environment,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.49,1:05:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but part of that is having to eliminate beavers at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.81,1:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm thinking this is one of those perception versus essence problems maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.37,1:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you have to eliminate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.54,1:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to be able to move them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.62,1:05:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to like end up going back from where I came
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.74,1:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and have God say, you know, you were doing so good up until that beaver thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.62,1:05:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You draw the line at that which you feel is a violation
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.24,1:05:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,of your understanding of the value of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.90,1:05:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can tell them, look, I'd be happy to move beavers all day long,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.64,1:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but killing them, I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.08,1:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I get into one of the thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.66,1:05:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the thoughts was you're probably just as guilty if you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.96,1:05:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do all the other stuff, but I'll have somebody else often.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.76,1:05:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can be a conscientious objector.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.32,1:05:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,During the war, we had a couple guys on the ship
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.98,1:05:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,that just didn't want to kill anybody,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.76,1:06:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but they don't mind doing the radio and doing the scribe.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.56,1:06:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could just say, look, I'm a conscientious objector.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.54,1:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't live with a conscience where I feel that I myself have done this.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.82,1:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.26,1:06:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough, tough one.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.12,1:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, maybe I should take up woodworking or something instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.96,1:06:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you just, you have to live with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.88,1:06:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you say, you know, it's going to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.37,1:06:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going to be done.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.61,1:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to be the one that does it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.05,1:06:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.92,1:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, World War II, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.84,1:06:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the greatest things for which I thank the Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.30,1:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is I didn't have to kill anybody, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.18,1:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a minesweeper.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.54,1:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to kill anybody.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.24,1:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would not envy somebody who's in the position where you gotta.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.73,1:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, if you gotta,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.69,1:07:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it's more or less taken out of your hands, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.41,1:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a difficult one.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.47,1:07:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I sympathize with your moral dilemma about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.94,1:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me something to think about anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.36,1:07:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.08,1:07:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be the one that pulls the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.48,1:07:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.78,1:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, you know, the guillotine's going to come down anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.64,1:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,14.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.46,1:07:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,14,000 were guillotined.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.16,1:07:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,14,000.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.89,1:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to be the one that runs the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.12,1:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither are you going to stop the French Revolution.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.09,1:07:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought you were going to stop the French Revolution
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.31,1:07:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and save the life of all the beavers.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.69,1:07:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't have to be you that runs the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.34,1:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.46,1:07:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get a beaver team.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.10,1:07:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Small, small-sized beaver-rama.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.84,1:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,14,000 people were chopped off for the guillotine.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.68,1:07:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.54,1:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.42,1:08:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been grappling all day over which of two questions to ask you,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.86,1:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I realize that they're related.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.80,1:08:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Three or four times now you've told me directly,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.04,1:08:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,one day I'll be looking at something and divinity will shine forth through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.43,1:08:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The other question, which will become obvious,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.99,1:08:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is how do you know when you're not playing in the astral domains?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.15,1:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm confused between...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.59,1:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Paradigms, almost, because particularly at night there are experiences
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.39,1:08:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,where what seemed harmless, just watching, have turned into not so harmless.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.91,1:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I guess I'm kind of confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.83,1:08:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, watching?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.03,1:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On television or in your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.95,1:08:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.29,1:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.75,1:08:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.67,1:08:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing what?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.07,1:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lights, energy patterns.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.27,1:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Visions of energy patterns and things like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.67,1:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.11,1:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they benign?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.27,1:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They were.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.47,1:09:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I would stick with the benign and refuse all others.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.69,1:09:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's okay, it's okay...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.53,1:09:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you can...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.45,1:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the testing of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.96,1:09:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Either it's benign and of the Christ or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.70,1:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can challenge the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.80,1:09:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called something, the qualification of the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.06,1:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To acknowledge Jesus Christ as your saviour, yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.10,1:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If it says no, you vanish it and get the hints.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.35,1:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.68,1:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.86,1:09:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got a formal name in religion.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.70,1:09:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The qualification or the declaration.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.58,1:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.26,1:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The provocation of the spirits?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.74,1:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows it?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.66,1:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody Christians here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.04,1:09:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called something.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.36,1:09:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a formal name.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.14,1:09:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All spirits can be challenged.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.92,1:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or the challenging of spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.63,1:09:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you acknowledge Jesus Christ as your saviour, yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.77,1:10:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.69,1:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If it says yes, then it is of the Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.79,1:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it could be, you know, like an angelic form.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.37,1:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is demonic will not acknowledge Jesus Christ as its saviour.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.46,1:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you can vanish it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.94,1:10:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not verbal or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.24,1:10:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But so...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.88,1:10:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you can hold that as a...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.30,1:10:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.18,1:10:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can hold it without verbalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.70,1:10:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.12,1:10:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.62,1:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You challenge the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.98,1:10:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not playing with the astral circus.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.70,1:10:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.24,1:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The circus is already going on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.70,1:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me what to do because it's going to enter us.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.46,1:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.24,1:10:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the screen doors.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.38,1:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what to do if they're already in the screen door.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.66,1:10:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just deny it all?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:39.18,1:10:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's just not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.32,1:10:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I would just challenge spirits or ignore them or order them henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.68,1:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean I'm distracted for lifetimes?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.88,1:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've warned against the astral circus and I don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.68,1:10:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, does this mean this is a distraction off of the goal?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.91,1:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.23,1:11:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can order them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.25,1:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can order them to leave you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.35,1:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In the name of the Lord Jesus Christ, I order you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.89,1:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.35,1:11:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.73,1:11:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can order them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.09,1:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You call upon the Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.63,1:11:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Banish them.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.30,1:11:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.77,1:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If Jesus Christ is your savior, is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.77,1:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.43,1:11:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you have the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.62,1:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all it takes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.34,1:11:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you go to church?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.80,1:11:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.12,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Used to.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.86,1:11:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a priest?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.95,1:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.59,1:11:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to let your priest go?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.69,1:11:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the side or what?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.07,1:11:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He was programming me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.45,1:11:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.98,1:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A conspiracy theorist.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.46,1:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.32,1:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.94,1:11:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.06,1:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.78,1:11:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I would just banish the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.10,1:11:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, you don't want them even if they're friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.10,1:11:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if they're friendly or not friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.12,1:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not equipped to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.62,1:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher says I should ask you to leave now.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.18,1:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.74,1:12:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.36,1:12:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back 20, 30 years, maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.14,1:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But in doing that, I'm not throwing the baby out with the bath.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.84,1:12:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, like I can just deny it all and it won't prevent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.50,1:12:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.02,1:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.46,1:12:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.90,1:12:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't reach enlightenment via that.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.18,1:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.12,1:12:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it distracting?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.42,1:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a distraction in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.21,1:12:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad we cleared that up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.25,1:12:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.39,1:12:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.93,1:12:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll test you out to see if you're friendly
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.53,1:12:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,until they're hanging around and fooling them and playing games with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.01,1:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you tell them you're not, they'll leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.81,1:12:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.83,1:12:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It just was so benign.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.07,1:12:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nothing before.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.59,1:12:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.15,1:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.73,1:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.19,1:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.65,1:12:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.17,1:12:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.15,1:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.47,1:12:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.51,1:12:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.98,1:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're seductive by their presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.89,1:12:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementals.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.69,1:12:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Elementals want to play games with their head.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.37,1:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.67,1:12:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.56,1:12:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seduce her into playing with them.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.04,1:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.40,1:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.48,1:12:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.12,1:12:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.11,1:12:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.29,1:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.41,1:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been experiencing a lot of changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.58,1:13:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was happening is I used to be very career-oriented,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.62,1:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,very success-oriented.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.19,1:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.45,1:13:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.43,1:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All my beliefs have fallen away.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.75,1:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel I know anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.83,1:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm left with no beliefs and not knowing anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.97,1:13:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And right now, I'm trying to go back to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.23,1:13:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know what direction to take.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.31,1:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have a work that we're supposed to be doing, something we're meant to do, a purposeful
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.65,1:13:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,work?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.91,1:13:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Or does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.71,1:13:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's within yourself, your own interests and capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.27,1:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And you dedicate it to the good of mankind and whatever service you can be, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.71,1:13:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to make a living.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.56,1:13:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your obligation.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.76,1:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're the steward of this body.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.20,1:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've got to keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.80,1:14:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, basically, I'm intelligent, I have skills, I mean, just use those skills.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.82,1:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I would use your skills and do what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.66,1:14:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have mechanical skills, artistic skills, whatever they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.20,1:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this work?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.06,1:14:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, will the, will the, you know, ask God for help, ask God for a miracle, and then it will help to bring me the job?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.05,1:14:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I go out and look, and I apply to everything?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.39,1:14:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Both will happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.09,1:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Both will happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.85,1:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, with spiritual help.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.35,1:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,With spiritual help, that which you seek, you'll find, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.19,1:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So take action, you say.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.23,1:14:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, they always say take action.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.35,1:14:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, always say take action.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.14,1:14:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I prayed for a job, and nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.38,1:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hadn't been for my brother-in-law calling me and offering me a job, I'd still be out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.42,1:14:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.72,1:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.48,1:14:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.26,1:15:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.14,1:15:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.14,1:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.74,1:15:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.65,1:15:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed today you calibrated broccoli, and broccoli is doing really well.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.03,1:15:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.22,1:15:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I've heard you say back in November that cats and dogs might have an etheric brain, and you didn't know because you hadn't asked.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.96,1:15:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.76,1:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was wondering if you would ask.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.62,1:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.44,1:15:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.26,1:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, we've got to know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.38,1:15:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just accept their lovingness as a gift and appreciate them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.42,1:15:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.02,1:15:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something yet that I don't know about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.02,1:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:01.29,1:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.29,1:16:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering about their evolution since broccoli is doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.29,1:16:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.29,1:16:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Broccoli is a different kind of energy than a cat or a dog.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:09.29,1:16:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.29,1:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more intellectual, mental, although she's very affectionate, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.29,1:16:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.29,1:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.29,1:16:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.29,1:16:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering about the spiritual evolution of cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.29,1:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.29,1:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.29,1:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.29,1:16:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.45,1:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I sort of have intuitive presumptions about it, but it's something I don't want to know about now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.90,1:16:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.90,1:16:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.90,1:16:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe 50, 100 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.90,1:16:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.90,1:16:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:35.90,1:16:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.90,1:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I go to Doggyland?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.90,1:16:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're obviously a gift to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.90,1:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people would have committed suicide if it wasn't for their pet.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.90,1:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.04,1:16:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Huggins.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.04,1:16:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.36,1:16:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you to describe Joppa, playing Joppa.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.36,1:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Joppa?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.36,1:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.36,1:16:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to know about it?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.93,1:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to know if I'm doing it right and if ...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.93,1:16:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.93,1:16:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.93,1:16:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.93,1:16:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.93,1:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.64,1:16:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.64,1:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.64,1:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a Joppa teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.64,1:17:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.64,1:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it ... I don't do it consistently, and that's maybe partly why I wanted to ask you
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.64,1:17:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.64,1:17:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I wanted to ... I think I wanted to know if I really should continue to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.64,1:17:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What attracted you to it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.64,1:17:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.64,1:17:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it helps me kind of not be frightened sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.76,1:17:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.76,1:17:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It helps me to stay focused, that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.76,1:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it calibrates well, so it's the same as I think it's praying, saying the Lord's
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.76,1:17:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Prayer.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.76,1:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.76,1:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.76,1:17:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.76,1:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.76,1:17:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.76,1:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.76,1:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.76,1:17:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.40,1:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.40,1:17:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.40,1:17:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.40,1:17:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.40,1:17:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.40,1:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.40,1:17:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.40,1:17:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.40,1:17:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.40,1:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.40,1:17:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.40,1:17:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.40,1:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.40,1:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.40,1:17:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.40,1:17:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.40,1:17:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,About the same effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.40,1:17:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.40,1:17:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so it's like a ..
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.40,1:17:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It pulls up that spiritual energy, and then that spiritual energy, where would
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.40,1:17:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,it look frightening or a problem, doesn't look frightening like a problem.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.40,1:17:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.40,1:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, actually, that's what it does for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.40,1:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, because it pulls up that energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.40,1:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And is it in the sound that that happens?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.40,1:17:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't researched it to that detail.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.42,1:17:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.42,1:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that helps, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.38,1:17:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why ..
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.38,1:17:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.38,1:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It pulls up that field because of the intention, and that field, then recontextualizes
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.14,1:17:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and reframes it, so it looks different.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.40,1:18:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.40,1:18:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Up, up, up, up, up, up, buddy. Remember in kindergarten? Up, up, up, up, buddy, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.65,1:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Dr. Hawkins. Before I started reading your books, which I consider my most practical
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.04,1:18:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual help now, I studied the works of L.S.A. Bailey and Helena Polatsky since my
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.62,1:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,youth, and I enjoyed particularly their exposition on cosmology, cosmogenesis, and so on, which
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.50,1:18:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't get into. I was just wondering, I didn't see them on your slide about spiritual
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.10,1:19:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,teachers. How would you rate them? I didn't have the White Brotherhood on there, no, or
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.54,1:19:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice Bailey, no. I didn't have the White Brotherhood. Or the Theosophical Teachings
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.10,1:19:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,as such. Oh, Theosophical, yes, yes. Polatsky in particular has, you know, the Secret Doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.08,1:19:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I didn't do Polatsky, no. I consider she's way up there. And Alice Bailey, of course,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.13,1:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of her.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.51,1:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other works were Cosmic Fire, which gets into cosmology. It's just marvelous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.95,1:19:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in becoming enlightened, not cosmology.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.82,1:19:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a particular field which interests me, but what you have to offer is the most
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.88,1:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,practical, the most helpful. So if in the future time, if in the future time you decide
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.79,1:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate those.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.79,1:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't do them all. You know, we did Alice Bailey's book Glamour, and I did Alice
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.79,1:19:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bailey's.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.79,1:19:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.63,1:20:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it explains a lot that without that explanation would be more harder to understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.63,1:20:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.63,1:20:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.63,1:20:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.63,1:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I respect the White Brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.63,1:20:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.63,1:20:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for being here. A little closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.63,1:20:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.63,1:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, I've been studying your work for several years, and this haunting question
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.98,1:20:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,has come back that I suspect is problematic.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.18,1:20:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.18,1:20:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What I suspect is probably my ego's, the fear of the death of the ego. And it's around,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.34,1:20:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wrote it so that I wouldn't, because it was very hard for me to put these thoughts
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.44,1:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.44,1:20:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.44,1:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about my recall of some of the writings that you have talked about over 600, when
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.18,1:21:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we have no more form after we leave this body. That there's, after 600, even up to the 50,000,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.34,1:21:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it, the Archangels at 50,000?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.18,1:21:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.18,1:21:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no form.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.18,1:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.18,1:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And so that means there's no experiencer. That means, of course, there's no-
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.18,1:21:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no what?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.18,1:21:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No experiencer.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.22,1:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.22,1:21:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.22,1:21:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.22,1:21:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the question is, how does one know that we exist without an experiencer?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.22,1:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There is the knowingness of existence without experiencing. Because you're already
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.85,1:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,putting non-ego in terms of the ego, and then asking me how come.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.13,1:21:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:43.13,1:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the manipulation of the thought form, see? The knowingness of existence is
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.27,1:22:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,not a me knowing of that fact. That means the ego would still persist. There would be
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.17,1:22:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,me, the ego, making a statement about its state called existence. You see, the dualistic.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.77,1:22:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no this being a that, see? The thing is what it is, and it's completely fulfilled
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.53,1:22:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in what it is without making a statement. It doesn't say I am. It does not say I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.15,1:22:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It just is. So, its existence is at one with its form. So, having form doesn't preclude
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.70,1:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,except that it doesn't know that. It has no consciousness. So, there's the conscious
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.80,1:22:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,awareness of existence without form. In fact, in that conscious awareness is the awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.16,1:23:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's because of I, consciousness, that any awareness of form can take place. Without
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.56,1:23:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,me, there would be no form. Without the knower of the form, there is no form. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.64,1:23:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, does that explain what happens when we go into the void then, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.96,1:23:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.96,1:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No? Because we still try to manufacture some kind of form when we go in? No?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.18,1:23:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the void?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.18,1:23:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, but I guess that's the fear the ego has somewhere along the line that if there's
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.50,1:23:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,no form.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.50,1:23:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego fears nothingness. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.50,1:23:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. And so, that's what all of this revolves around.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.50,1:23:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it hangs on to form because it thinks without form it will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.50,1:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.50,1:23:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.50,1:23:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.50,1:23:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a fact. It will.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.98,1:23:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.88,1:23:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it feels fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.88,1:24:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, indeed it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.43,1:24:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.43,1:24:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, indeed it is. Then the ego is.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.43,1:24:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, then you experience out the fear. And then, because all fear is illusion, the truth
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.78,1:24:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,takes the place of the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.78,1:24:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Experience it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.32,1:24:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.98,1:24:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.98,1:24:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego feels that without form it will cease to exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.98,1:24:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.98,1:24:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it identifies the form.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.98,1:24:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.98,1:24:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.98,1:24:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.08,1:24:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's got more to say besides form.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.08,1:24:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.08,1:24:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. It's got more to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.08,1:24:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.08,1:24:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell the ego, you won't run out of juice when you run out of form. You'll think of
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.08,1:24:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,some other sneaky way to be around it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.08,1:24:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll claim to be the author of formlessness, so you'll see. It's got more games.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.08,1:24:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got more games in its pocket to pull out.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.08,1:24:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.08,1:24:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.08,1:24:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up that.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.08,1:24:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.08,1:24:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.08,1:24:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.77,1:24:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.77,1:24:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.77,1:24:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.77,1:24:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.77,1:24:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.77,1:24:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.77,1:24:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.77,1:24:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.22,1:24:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.28,1:24:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.28,1:24:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.72,1:25:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.34,1:25:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.81,1:25:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.81,1:25:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.81,1:25:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.80,1:25:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.80,1:25:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.80,1:25:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.80,1:25:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.80,1:25:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.80,1:25:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.80,1:25:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your book has brought tremendous joy to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.80,1:25:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.80,1:25:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It opened my eyes to other teachings that I did not have the validity from them to know
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.56,1:25:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was truth in that material.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.60,1:25:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.60,1:25:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.56,1:25:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the things I'm starting to experience is fear in meditation, that there's something
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.64,1:25:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,after me.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.26,1:25:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.36,1:25:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced it a week ago when I was in the woods of Virginia, alone at night, and in the silence, the fear came up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.51,1:25:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh-huh. That's the child coming up in you. That was the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.84,1:25:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.76,1:26:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the child? That's the child coming up. Yeah, it was the child coming up in you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.68,1:26:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What avenue should I pursue to find what is bringing that up? I'll call you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.90,1:26:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You speak to the child in reassuring terms, and know that all fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.16,1:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.74,1:26:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to persist fear of what?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.80,1:26:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.67,1:26:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of fear?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.41,1:26:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of fear, or fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.41,1:26:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Yeah, well, just keep surrendering that, and it'll negate itself. It'll resolve itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.23,1:26:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because all fear is based on illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.79,1:26:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.00,1:26:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the risk is going to happen to you as you die.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.70,1:26:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You said, yeah, well, wouldn't that make you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.96,1:26:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You don't have to be afraid of dying, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.40,1:26:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I'm saying? You can chase fear right down to its nub, and undo it.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.59,1:26:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I will practice that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.51,1:27:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, one other I may ask. There's a lot of information that you've brought forth to this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.70,1:27:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives us credence. How would you like to see, excuse me, back up.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.25,1:27:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in and out of AA. I'm familiar with Bill Williams.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.71,1:27:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.91,1:27:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I went back with a friend that had been...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.19,1:27:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,using drugs, and been back into the meetings.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.51,1:27:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see it as being a springboard that could be used to increase the spiritual awareness on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.43,1:27:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.65,1:27:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it does calculate at 540.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.59,1:27:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure. That's pretty high.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.37,1:27:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you given it, or considered, or looked in that direction on how you would like to see your material increased on this planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.31,1:27:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And one that I see is in chaos at some points, in ignorance, and have problems coming ahead of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.07,1:27:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.21,1:27:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Or have problems that...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.35,1:27:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Or have problems that might come ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.33,1:27:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where, the planet?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.49,1:27:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the near future, the planet itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.69,1:28:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Well, I think grassroots spirituality is based on practical, experiential reality such as the 12-step groups...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.50,1:28:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.26,1:28:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...have a subtle profound effect that seeps out into society.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.80,1:28:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think AA actually influences society. One reason we calibrate what we do is because of the influence of AA subtly on all kinds of ways which people don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.06,1:28:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.64,1:28:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.08,1:28:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...people don't know the announcer they're listening to.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.16,1:28:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.58,1:28:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been sober 22 years, and they don't know who's in AA.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.48,1:28:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But that integrity spreads out as an example to the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.86,1:28:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I think it uplifts mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.56,1:28:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think the consciousness of America would be the same without AA.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.44,1:28:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I see that from where I'm coming from,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.82,1:28:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see because of your association with Bill W. at one time
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.78,1:28:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that the group itself, if it was made aware,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.50,1:28:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,made is the wrong word, brought aware of the material that you've brought forward,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.48,1:28:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that it could grow a lot quicker than what it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.86,1:28:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they all blend together, and each one supports the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.40,1:28:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the miracles of AA and this work,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.02,1:29:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, they're grassroots.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.00,1:29:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a formal structure or building or anything,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.86,1:29:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and those kind of things tend to become more pervasive.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.57,1:29:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has structure and form tends to create a resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.73,1:29:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That which has no structure and no form
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.39,1:29:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and no...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.61,1:29:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No program and no agenda that's trying to sell anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.01,1:29:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't create resistance.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.47,1:29:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:26.49,1:29:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If a guy wants to be honest on the job
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.21,1:29:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and be an example to others by his honesty and his friendliness,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.49,1:29:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no defense against that.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.39,1:29:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't even know he's in AA, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.05,1:29:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have run into some resistance through some statements I've made,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.79,1:29:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,or subtle statements, but there is resistance to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.49,1:29:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.42,1:29:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's better not to label it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.14,1:29:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call it AA or anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.38,1:29:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.70,1:29:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.88,1:30:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.45,1:30:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.16,1:30:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For about maybe six months to a year now,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.14,1:30:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been kind of on a rollercoaster of going in and out of like
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.36,1:30:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what I consider like a high spiritual state
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.66,1:30:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then like a dropping into kind of a low depressive state,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.88,1:30:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe kind of like a dark night of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.20,1:30:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.18,1:30:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm curious if you have like any advice for...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.28,1:30:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're just living through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.74,1:30:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can expect that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.40,1:30:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.04,1:30:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because you rise above your karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.26,1:30:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, because of the good karma, you're entitled to bring up the next stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.58,1:30:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens is the next stack comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.64,1:30:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.88,1:30:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.28,1:30:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you've got the power and the strength now to handle that stack.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.78,1:30:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go through one stack after another.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.42,1:30:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They eventually clear up.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.76,1:30:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.72,1:30:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.60,1:31:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It can seem like a lot at times.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.02,1:31:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.72,1:31:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Last time I was here, I was telling you about my...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.80,1:31:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego issues, and you told me to not do, and I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.72,1:31:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I not did very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.74,1:31:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I quit my job, and life is in a very big changing moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.54,1:31:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But I feel that there's a concern that maybe this surrender is really maybe a recklessness,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.14,1:31:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,a shunning of spiritual responsibility maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:32.90,1:31:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's like my spiritual policeman saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.04,1:31:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, be on the ball.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.54,1:31:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, surrender means surrendering, trying to control the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.00,1:31:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the result.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.08,1:31:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But the effort, of course, is dependent on your spiritual level and your commitment.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.38,1:31:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the way I've been going about it is like surrendering to the current of the river of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.72,1:31:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.16,1:31:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And just flowing in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.96,1:31:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.44,1:31:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens, happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.80,1:31:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.48,1:31:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't know if maybe that's a little too cavalier,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.20,1:32:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or is that the ego is just begging for that last bit of control?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.24,1:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, you can't do it without me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.50,1:32:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, surrender is different than passivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.11,1:32:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.19,1:32:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think about that, or look at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.66,1:32:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because sometimes surrender means surrendering to a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.20,1:32:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, surrendering your resistance to the fact that you've got a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.20,1:32:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So look at those shades in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.94,1:32:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your problem is in there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.17,1:32:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That works for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.17,1:32:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.48,1:32:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.96,1:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirituality is more than truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.76,1:32:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't believe in politics.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.08,1:32:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't going to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.76,1:32:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And you go like another would say, well, my responsibility as a spiritually integrous person is to vote.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.04,1:32:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.56,1:32:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it depends on which facet of the diamond you're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.60,1:32:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.46,1:32:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.62,1:33:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a good friend that's becoming, like, increasingly negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.95,1:33:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to, like, play with fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.07,1:33:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's better to avoid him or to try to understand him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.08,1:33:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you understand what's going on with him, it can help.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.30,1:33:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only do that if you understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.72,1:33:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't understand and he's going into a negative direction,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.76,1:33:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you're probably going to have to part.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.69,1:33:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.19,1:33:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.28,1:33:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.76,1:33:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.76,1:33:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I brought you a thank you letter, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.19,1:33:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.82,1:33:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.60,1:33:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.48,1:33:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And in my own spiritual quest, I mean, I've kind of been trying to figure out what's the purpose of any negativity at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.52,1:34:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In the whole spectrum of reality, it seems like, okay, well, and I've thought of this, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.30,1:34:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,why not just existence and consciousness being so pure and perfect in its own essence?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.86,1:34:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, why?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.30,1:34:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.40,1:34:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.52,1:34:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.24,1:34:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why have this contradicting force that we have to go through?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:09.66,1:34:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And, like, the one thing that I have came to, like, the conclusion is maybe it's so you can actually recognize
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.90,1:34:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,how sweet enlightenment really is once you get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.40,1:34:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, it's so painful to have to go through it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.54,1:34:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I mean, I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:20.52,1:34:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Painful to go through what?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.80,1:34:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,To go through all of the downfalls and everything you have to, all of these, this craziness and madness
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.72,1:34:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,before you can actually get that clarity, which I'm starting to get.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.14,1:34:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.28,1:34:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, I mean, like, what is the ultimate?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.99,1:34:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to figure out what...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.99,1:34:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you say is the ultimate purpose of negativity in any way?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.27,1:34:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if God is the consciousness and love within everything...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.69,1:34:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.41,1:34:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.73,1:34:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's negativity doing there?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.09,1:34:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.33,1:34:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we looked at the chart showing the evolution of consciousness, and we saw that mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.08,1:35:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is on a rising curve, and you're part of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.62,1:35:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, along with mankind, you are, like, transcending the negatives.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:06.48,1:35:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The temptation to hate, you're turning it down now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.56,1:35:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The temptation for greed, you're turning it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.80,1:35:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The temptation for envy.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.02,1:35:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they have to come up for you to transcend them and turn them down.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.96,1:35:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't that they're bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.16,1:35:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you've made a decision to be otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.14,1:35:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.48,1:35:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.10,1:35:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.02,1:35:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's normal.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.16,1:35:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal what you're going through.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.38,1:35:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.83,1:35:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.05,1:35:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.92,1:35:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, 12-step groups, they call...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.66,1:35:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They have what they call the fourth step.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.20,1:35:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You take a spiritual inventory.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.84,1:35:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You take a long, yellow...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.13,1:35:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Legal-sized tablet.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.21,1:35:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You start writing down all your character defects.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.83,1:35:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.34,1:35:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.26,1:35:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In the book, Transcending Level of Consciousness, the section about temptations from different
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.16,1:36:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,level of consciousness, under this level, ecstasy, you list poor judgment as a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:07.65,1:36:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you please elaborate on this?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.05,1:36:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by poor judgment?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.51,1:36:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a temptation.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.63,1:36:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a temptation, but it's one quality that the downside of ecstasy is to lead to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.11,1:36:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,excessive behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.61,1:36:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excessive behaviors.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.85,1:36:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each side has its upside and its downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.63,1:36:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ecstasy could lead you to taking off all your clothes and deciding you can fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.27,1:36:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And people on LSD did that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.57,1:36:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They go in a state of ecstasy, take off their clothes, and expect to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.49,1:36:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the downside is brash foolishness.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.01,1:36:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you constantly surrender your ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.37,1:36:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The ecstasy is coming from the awareness of the presence of God as the source of your
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.23,1:36:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,existence, and the totality of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.59,1:37:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's ecstatic when that suddenly dawns on you, because it breaks through, like, overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.06,1:37:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're just stunned by it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.42,1:37:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the possibility would be to go into an ecstatic state and have it mistaken as catatonia
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.41,1:37:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.01,1:37:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me put you away.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.55,1:37:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what can we do to kind of guard against that kind of irrationality?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.63,1:37:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.57,1:37:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.25,1:37:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If they put you away, you haven't called me, I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.17,1:37:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good advice.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.21,1:37:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.59,1:37:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.49,1:37:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.93,1:37:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is in a state of ecstasy.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.27,1:37:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do with him, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.35,1:37:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.21,1:37:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to quit now.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.83,1:37:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.25,1:37:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got just a couple more.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.41,1:37:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got four minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.85,1:37:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we do.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.41,1:37:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's four minutes to five.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.19,1:37:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.85,1:37:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.39,1:37:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got four minutes to five.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.15,1:37:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine is atomic time.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.49,1:37:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.11,1:37:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to hurry, folks.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.69,1:37:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.61,1:37:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.13,1:38:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.69,1:38:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been studying the keys of Enoch.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.92,1:38:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You did not calibrate it very high.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.44,1:38:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was drawn to it because of the level of scientific complexity and the possibilities
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.19,1:38:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of connecting with someone who has been or re-spatialized to higher levels of being.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.53,1:38:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.59,1:38:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you comment on this any more about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.17,1:38:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We calibrated the keys of Enoch and all I can tell you is what it calibrated at.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.17,1:38:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget now.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.93,1:38:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's in the book, Truth Versus Falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.19,1:38:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.95,1:38:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And have you experienced the other, you were talking about the low levels that you're not
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.41,1:38:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrating, but have you experienced yourself higher levels with the ascended masters and
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.59,1:38:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the grids of being?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.27,1:38:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See, those are celestial realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.87,1:38:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go into the realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.10,1:38:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They all have their own hierarchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.81,1:38:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's possible for us as humans to go there?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.91,1:38:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's an infinite number of celestial realms and other dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.87,1:38:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In this lifetime, I don't have the time to go into them because what can any one of them
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.73,1:39:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,offer you?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.43,1:39:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.03,1:39:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than enlightenment, none of them have anything to offer you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.41,1:39:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So leave the celestial realms.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.11,1:39:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From this dimension, you can reach salvation through Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.73,1:39:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reach the enlightenment through the pathway of the Buddha.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.01,1:39:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:18.52,1:39:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reach Krishna consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.90,1:39:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So what does another dimension?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.52,1:39:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That to offer you other than novelty and cutesy ideas and weird names for the divinity of
Dialogue: 0,1:39:26.34,1:39:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that dimension, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:28.06,1:39:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ponder that.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:30.31,1:39:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing beyond salvation, redemption, and enlightenment, is there?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.85,1:39:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the keys to any kind of a weird other dimension going to offer you other than
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.82,1:39:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,novelty?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:45.40,1:39:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say I call the head of my dimension Ugg.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.56,1:39:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.34,1:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We all worship Ugg.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.29,1:39:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.26,1:39:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, you don't live in that dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.28,1:39:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You live in this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.96,1:40:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So Ugg isn't going to do you any good anyway because you're not an Ugg-ian.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.90,1:40:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I live in Ugg.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.40,1:40:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a human-ian.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.40,1:40:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Jesus Christ, you've got the Buddha, you've got Krishna, what more do you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.56,1:40:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.56,1:40:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we do have...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.69,1:40:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for big animals and you've got an elephant in your living room.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.45,1:40:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.45,1:40:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you pushing me for?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:17.48,1:40:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not under a compulsion to walk out the door at this stroke.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.48,1:40:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only got a couple of people left.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.48,1:40:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.13,1:40:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.13,1:40:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.13,1:40:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.13,1:40:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.13,1:40:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:29.13,1:40:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.13,1:40:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.13,1:40:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.87,1:40:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, move along.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.92,1:40:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.92,1:40:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let me thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.92,1:40:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.92,1:40:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've helped contextualize what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.24,1:40:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a 28-day program when I realized that I was in the same boat as everybody else,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.82,1:41:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and that really I couldn't really...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.90,1:41:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know any of the truth from falsehood.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.20,1:41:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.20,1:41:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And neither did anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.47,1:41:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.47,1:41:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I went on my knees, and I just asked to just know, like to get better.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.44,1:41:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.42,1:41:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I lost track of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.78,1:41:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And how could I put that?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.69,1:41:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt this energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.73,1:41:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I could connect with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.20,1:41:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And the therapist knew that there was something fairly drastic happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.77,1:41:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I knew that I couldn't function in the world like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:43.73,1:41:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I still had young kids at home.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.66,1:41:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And he asked me to pull back, because I was going to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.74,1:41:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't think I could function.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.23,1:42:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So I did pull back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.64,1:42:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there to listen to what I was told.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.34,1:42:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.88,1:42:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I listened.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.33,1:42:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pulled back, went back to my mind, thinking and everything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:12.47,1:42:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even have to think then.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.45,1:42:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know what happened, though.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.27,1:42:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.80,1:42:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In reading your books now, I do know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.78,1:42:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.60,1:42:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back at that point now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.62,1:42:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Back to what point?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.67,1:42:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That I can just feel the energy up my back.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.63,1:42:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All over, it's burning.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.81,1:42:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you recovered from the purpose for which you went there?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.37,1:42:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I haven't had a drink, nothing ever since.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.79,1:42:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.09,1:42:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.67,1:42:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning in.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:47.68,1:42:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, the question that I have is this here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.10,1:42:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the point where I feel like what I have to do next...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.92,1:43:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just feel the energy and just do what I do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.16,1:43:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.72,1:43:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.88,1:43:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And just feel the energy and don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.60,1:43:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just feel it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.40,1:43:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.96,1:43:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:09.29,1:43:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.72,1:43:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.68,1:43:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good spot on the turn around, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.82,1:43:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:23.70,1:43:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I started on my spiritual path, I had a relatively good sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.57,1:43:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm starting to take things so seriously.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.51,1:43:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Suggestions for recouping my sense of humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.13,1:43:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So logically, I've done.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.50,1:43:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.28,1:43:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a period where you go through it serious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.90,1:43:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's a period where it's humorous again.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.50,1:43:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And later on, you get serious about your humor.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.62,1:43:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you think getting serious about your humor itself is humorous.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.48,1:44:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which in itself is a serious matter, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.88,1:44:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.26,1:44:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think humor is of divine origin.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.38,1:44:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all done, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.96,1:44:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.30,1:44:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.44,1:44:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.47,1:44:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:20.38,1:44:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Huggins.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:21.20,1:44:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd first like to thank you for your teachings and you've helped me a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.76,1:44:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what I would do without you, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.14,1:44:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a question about my own intentions, my own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.74,1:44:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.72,1:44:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just worried my own intentions, I'm worried about my own intentions and my own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.92,1:44:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own what?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.78,1:44:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Intentions.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.60,1:44:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Intentions?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.52,1:44:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.46,1:44:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.44,1:44:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Your motivations.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.80,1:44:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Use different languages.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.04,1:44:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention doesn't mean much to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.14,1:44:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.78,1:44:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to, what's your goal?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.30,1:44:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Define your intention by your goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.80,1:44:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.28,1:44:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,To be more loving, more patient.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.40,1:44:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:59.70,1:45:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,More generous towards others.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.23,1:45:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask for a miracle instead of trying to control things.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:06.98,1:45:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.74,1:45:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.62,1:45:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You just apply that everywhere you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.08,1:45:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.39,1:45:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.89,1:45:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the consequences will come about as a result of what you've become.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.37,1:45:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The field begins to expand.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.87,1:45:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the field lifts you like a balloon.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.24,1:45:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.78,1:45:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't like you cause yourself to rise.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.04,1:45:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:25.68,1:45:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But by the raising of your spiritual intention, you like change your buoyancy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.60,1:45:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you sort of begin to float up in the field where the same field other people have drowned, you float.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.02,1:45:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.54,1:45:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll see others drown in the same field in which you float.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.36,1:45:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.90,1:45:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.62,1:45:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.22,1:45:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.84,1:45:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.81,1:45:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.27,1:45:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it some go down and others go up in exactly the same field?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.41,1:45:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.97,1:45:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.79,1:45:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because your intention, your buoyancy is different.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.97,1:45:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.40,1:45:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.60,1:45:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.62,1:45:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.86,1:46:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.34,1:46:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:10.08,1:46:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to Almighty God for the joy of your presence and your love, which is God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:22.78,1:46:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.10,1:46:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God, for all these wonderful people.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.66,1:46:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.70,1:46:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.
